name: Doge Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: The Doge community has always been about fun and humor. We propose a move from a more hobby driven blockchain technology to the most secure and advanced: Stellar. We saw a lot of opportunities with Dogecoin, but due to it’s shrinking community we build an alternative: Doge Token.
